	<td class="bodycopy">
		<!--BODYCOPY BEGINS HERE-->

<p>
The Shift Left and Shift Right variants were designed by Josh Smith.
The Shift Around variant (identical to Shift Right except that Austria
and Russia exchange their starting positions) was created by Dan
Dzikowicz.


